DOM Events 
===========
is an action that happens in the browser and JS to respond it 
* user clicks a button 
* user types in an input 
* user submits a form
* the page finishes loading 
* moving a mouse over an element 

Basic Event flow
======================
step1: select an element
step2: Attach an event listener
step3: write what should happen once the action happen

